3. Dependencies

	* Webserver that supports
	  * rewrites
	  * php
	* MySQL
	* PHP 5.1+ with 
	  * PHP-GD
	  * PHP-MySQL
	* Cron or method to schedule regular script runs
	* BASH shell for CLI scripts

